rComments: Really easy class! She is really sweet and she will help you with whatever you need. Even if you don't like to speak in front of people I really recommend getting into her section.

First impression was not great. She talked about her cats and political science a lot. She is ridiculously easy on grades and a genuinely nice person. Highly recommend to take her section if at all possible. I'm fairly sure that everyone in our section will end up with an A.
